data.description: Welcome to 9622 Crail! This charming home is ready for you to make it your own. Located in the peaceful Gleanloch subdivision, you'll enjoy the tranquility of this established neighborhood. With easy access to HWY 249, Beltway 8, and Grand Parkway, commuting is a breeze. Inside, you'll find a fresh looking home throughout with a bright and inviting atmosphere. The granite-topped kitchen opens up to the breakfast and living rooms, creating a perfect space for entertaining. The primary bathroom features two separate sinks and vanities, adding convenience to your daily routine. With quick access to restaurants and shopping, as well as being minutes away from major highways and The Woodlands, you'll have everything you need right at your fingertips. Don't miss out on this outstanding opportunity to own a home in the highly sought-after Klein School District!
